quran[19]{c,v,t}:
  8,22,"Mu vy’ukuri ibikoko bibi imbere y’Imana nivyahawe ukutumva, n’abihaye kuba ari ibiragi, n’ukutabishira mubwenge bwabo"
  8,23,"Iyo Imana imenya ineza iyariyo yose kuribo, yari kubumvisha naho yari kubumvisha bari guhinduka nukutavyitaho"
  8,24,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimwitabe Imana hamwe n’intumwa yayo mugihe ibahamagariye kubintu vyobaha ubuzima bwiza, kandi mumenye yuko Imana y’injira hagati y’umuntu n’umutima wiwe nukubaho kwiwe, niwe niho muzokwegeranywa mwese"
  8,25,"Kandi mutinye ibihano vy’Imana vy’aha kw’Isi bitazobashikira bonyene mubahemukiye imitima yabo muri mwebwe, kandi mumenye yuko Imana ikaze cane muguhana"
  8,26,"Mwibuke mugihe mwari inkehwa muboneka yuko mugoyagoya kuri iy’Isi, mutinya abantu kugira ngo ntimufatwe, mugabo Imana iha ahantu heza hukubaho, n’ukubaha ishaka ry’uburokoke bwayo, n’ukubaha imigisha myiza kugira ngo mushobore gukenguruka"
  8,27,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, ntimuhemukire Imana yanyu y’ukuri hamwe n’intumwa y’ayo, kandi ntimuhemukire amaziganyo yanyu namwe mubizi"
  8,28,"Mumenye yuko amatungo yanyu hamwe n’ibibondo vyanyu ari ibibazo kuri mwebwe, kandi mumenye yuko ku Mana hariho impembo niniya cane"
  8,29,"Mwebwe mwemeye Imana yanyu y’ukuri, nimwagamburukira Imana yanyu y’ukuri izobaha itandukanyo ry’ugutandukanya ibiri hagati y’ukuri n’ikinyoma, kandi izoba hanagurira amakosa yanyu n’ukubagirira ikigongwe, n’Imana niyo nyene imigisha mininiya cane"
  8,30,"No mugihe bakugirira imigambi bamwe bahakana Imana yabo y’ukuri kugira ngo bakubohe canke bakugandagure canke bagukure mugisagara cawe, baca bagira imigambi iboneka, n’Imana ica ibahindurira iyo migambi yabo, n’Imana niyo nziza y’uguhindura imigambi y’abantu babi"
  8,31,"Mugihe basomewe amajambo yacu matagatifu baca bavuga bati:- turamaze kuyumva kuva kera, rero iyo dushaka twari kuvuga nk’aya majambo, ibi rero ntanakimwe birimwo ahubwo n’imigani yaba kera"
  8,32,"No mugihe bavuga bati:- ewe Mana yacu nivyaba ibi ari ivy’ukuri bivuye kuri wewe n’udushungurire imvura y’isegenya ivuye mw’ijuru kandi utuzanire ibindi bihano bibabaza gusumba ivyo"
  8,33,"Mugabo Imana ntiyari kubahana mugihe wewe wari kumwe nabo, canke n’Imana ntiyari kubahana mugihe nabo bariko barasaba ikigongwe"
  8,34,"Mugabo bafise ijambo nyabaki kugeza naho Imana itobahana mugihe bazitira abantu n’iryo sengero ritagatifu, nabo batari abaricungera, ntibari abaricungera atari abagamburukira Imana bonyene gusa, mugabo benshi muribo ntanakimwe bazi"
  8,35,"Kandi ntiyari kuba amasengesho yabo muri iryo sengero ritagatifu atari ukuvuza uruhwa hamwe n’ugukoma amashi, rero ni muhonje ibihano kubera ubuhakanyi bwanyu"
  8,36,"Mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahakanye Imana yabo y’ukuri, bahora batanga amatungo yabo kugira ngo bazitire inzira y’Imana rero bazoyatanga ayo matungo yabo munyuma yaho hazoba ari umwidogo kuribo hanyuma bazotsindwa, nabamwe bagumye mubuhakanyi bwabo bazokwegeranywa mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu"
  8,37,"Kugira ngo Imana ibatandukanye abantu babi hamwe n’abantu beza, n’ugushira abantu babi hejuru y’abandi bantu babi hamwe nukubegeranya bose hamwe nukubata mu muriro udahera witiriwe Jahannamu, abo bantu nibo bari muruhombo"
  8,38,"N’ubwire abo bahakanyi b’Imana y’ukuri nibareka kugira amabi, bazogirirwa ikigongwe n’ivy’akahise kuribo, mugabo nibasubira kuribo uburorero nk’ubwo buzoba bwaraheze bw’abantu baho hambere"
  8,39,"Nimurwane nabo kugeza aho hatazoba ibihano, hanyuma idini ibeho kubera Imana, mugabo nibareka bamenye yuko Imana ibona ivyo bagira vyose"
  8,40,"Nibahindukira muce mumenya yuko Imana ariyo Muremyi wanyu, kandi ariwe Muremyi mwiza n’umufasha mwiza"